HEADWORD: Monochromic
<hw>Mon`o*chro"mic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Made, or done,
with a single color; <as>as, a <ex>monochromic</ex> picture</as>. Called
also, <altname>monochromatic</altname> and
<altname>monochrome</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Monochromy</ent>⟦br⟧
